2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"我们对今天上午的局势感到非常失望和悲伤。 北京的支持者在立法机关中的行为，以及立法机关秘书处的政治助手（事件？），都是可鄙的。 当然，罪魁祸首是林嘉欣，他非常努力，对所有人来说都是如此显而易见，试图推行这项所谓的逃犯法，即所谓的逃犯法，将香港的利益卖给河流。 通过她在立法机关的暴徒和暴徒，他们试图扭曲所有的房屋规则和所有我们所谓的规则，以适应他们的目的 - 这就是今天早上造成混乱局面的原因。 但我们民主党人会继续战斗。 我需要强调的一件事是，我们的同事Gary Fan现在在玛丽医院急诊室。 但他应该没问题，他只是进行了CT扫描，显然他是有意识的。 所以我们希望他毕竟基本上都很好。"},{"pid":"2e925caf00e37f6fc66605d9a1b6a150e68d05b9","tid":1149273,"uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>We are quite disappointed and saddened by the situation this morning. The behavior of the Beijing loyalists at this legislature, complete with the political assistants&rsquo; (affair?) from the legislature&rsquo;s secretariat, is just contemptible. The culprit number one, definitely, is Carrie Lam, who tries so hard, so obvious to all, to try to push through this evil law, this so-called fugitives law, that would sell Hong Kong&rsquo;s interests down the river. And through her goons and thugs at the legislature, they are trying to twist all the house rules and all our supposed regulations in order to fit their end &ndash; and that&rsquo;s what&rsquo;s caused the chaotic situation this morning. But we the democrats will fight on. One thing I need to stress, is our colleague Gary Fan is now at the Queen Mary Hospital emergency room. But he should be okay, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">he&rsquo;s just has the CT scan</span></strong></span>, and apparently he&rsquo;s conscious. <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">So we wish he&rsquo;s basically well</span></span></strong> after all.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果咁basic 既grammar 都錯都幾難J<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heh